# tibxfrontsms

## Project uses typescript
https://www.typescriptlang.org/

## Project config
`src/config/settings.local.ts`

## How to start project locally
1. Install all npm dependencies from package.json

    [VS Code](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/35563802/running-npm-command-within-visual-studio-code)

    [WebStorm](https://www.jetbrains.com/help/webstorm/installing-and-removing-external-software-using-node-package-manager.html)
    
    Terminal
    ```bash
    npm install
    ```
    
2. Use 'start' script from package.json this will start local sever on port 3000

    [VS Code](https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/editor/tasks)
    
    [WebStorm](https://www.jetbrains.com/help/webstorm/installing-and-removing-external-software-using-node-package-manager.html#ws_npm_running_npm_scripts)
    
    Terminal
    ```bash
    npm run start
    ```

### Compiles and hot-reloads for development
```
npm run start
```

### Compiles and minifies for production
```
npm run build
```

### Run your tests
```
npm run test
```

### Lints and fixes files
```
npm run lint:ts:fix
npm run lint:css:fix
npm run prettier
```

### Analyze chunks
Install webpack-bundle-analyzer before using this 
```
npm run analyzer
```

### Structure
1. src - project source
2. src/assets - project resources (global css, fonts, images)
3. src/classes - project business logic
4. src/models - frontend objects for representing business entities
5. src/services - classes for actions on models and other business logic
6. src/components - project react components (view)
7. src/components/shared - project specific components. Can be reused between components
8. src/config - project configs
9. src/store - project redux

